description: Demolition of the existing 2 residential buildings for medical staff, comprising 358 studio flats and 360 sqm nursery and the erection of a part two, part four & part 6 storey building to provide 119 residential flats (30x1 bed, 54x2 bed, 25x3 bed 8x4 bed and 2x5 bed) and 423 sqm nursery.
